(4867, 5, '2014-06-08 13:13:39', '2014-06-08 13:13:39', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 2 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. In this part Tidus continues to chat to Rikku about the world he finds himself in, and before long they are interrupted by our old friend Sin. Tidus wakes up having drifted to the shore of a tropical island. A man with crazy orange hair spots him and flings a blitzball at his head, maybe this time Tidus will find himself closer to home?</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 2 - Besaid Island', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-2-besaid-island', '', '', '2014-06-08 13:13:39', '2014-06-08 13:13:39', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-2-besaid-island/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4868, 5, '2014-06-08 13:15:04', '2014-06-08 13:15:04', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 3 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. Tidus is introduced to the village of Besaid. He enters the temple and starts to realise how different this world is from his own. He later falls asleep, and it is revealed that a summoner is inside the cloister of trails and has not returned. Tidus hears of this and heroically decides to ignore the precepts of Yevon and heads into the trials to save the summoner.<br />Al Bhed Primer number 2 is picked up in this video.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 3 - The First Cloister', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-3-the-first-cloister', '', '', '2014-06-08 13:15:04', '2014-06-08 13:15:04', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-3-the-first-cloister/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4869, 5, '2014-06-08 13:16:44', '2014-06-08 13:16:44', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />I look forward to the inevitable discussion that will ensue about the lovely ladies of FFX :P Welcome to part 4 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. Wakka and Tidus head to the chamber of the fayth and inside find Yuna''s 2 other guardians, Lulu and Kimahri. Then the summoner emerges from the chamber, and it is not what Tidus was expecting. Summoner Yuna shows off her new aeon, and the two get to talk for the first time.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 4 - She''s Cute Ya?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-4-shes-cute-ya', '', '', '2014-06-08 13:16:44', '2014-06-08 13:16:44', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-4-shes-cute-ya/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4870, 5, '2014-06-08 13:17:51', '2014-06-08 13:17:51', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 5 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. Tidus and the gang say their goodbyes in Besaid and jump on a boat that will take them to their next stop, Kilika island.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 5 - Boat To Kilika', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-5-boat-to-kilika', '', '', '2014-06-08 13:17:51', '2014-06-08 13:17:51', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-5-boat-to-kilika/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4874, 5, '2014-06-08 13:24:00', '2014-06-08 13:24:00', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 6 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. The boat trip continues, and Tidus gets further acquainted with Yuna. Just when things are going swimmingly, our old friend Sin makes yet another appearance... Two boss battles in this video, Sin''s Fin and Sinspawn Euchilles.<br />Al Bhed Primer 3 is found in this video.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 6 - Sin''s Fin &amp; Euchilles', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-6-sins-fin-euchilles-2', '', '', '2014-06-08 13:24:00', '2014-06-08 13:24:00', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-6-sins-fin-euchilles-2/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4875, 5, '2014-06-08 13:27:33', '2014-06-08 13:27:33', '<p>Walkthrough Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLqxkRv1dWpjqVD2fJzgr4gBiiEQzyBTgT</p><p>StarCraft II: Wings of Liberty is a military science fiction real-time strategy video game developed and released by Blizzard Entertainment for Microsoft Windows and Mac OS X. A sequel to the award-winning 1998 video game StarCraft and its expansion set Brood War, the game was released worldwide on July 27, 2010.[6] It is split into three installments: the base game with the subtitle Wings of Liberty, an expansion pack Heart of the Swarm, as well as an upcoming expansion pack Legacy of the Void.[7]</p><p>The game revolves around three species: the Terrans, human exiles from Earth; the Zerg, a super-species of assimilated life forms;[8] and the Protoss, a technologically advanced species with vast mental powers. Wings of Liberty focuses on the Terrans, while the expansions Heart of the Swarm and Legacy of the Void will focus on the Zerg and Protoss, respectively. The game is set four years after the events of 1998''s StarCraft: Brood War, and follows the exploits of Jim Raynor as he leads an insurgent group against the autocratic Terran Dominion. The game includes both new and returning characters and locations from the original game.</p><p>Please Like and Subscribe.</p>', 'Starcraft 2 Wings of Liberty Walkthrough Part 1 Liberation Day Commentary', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'starcraft-2-wings-of-liberty-walkthrough-part-1-liberation-day-commentary', '', '', '2014-06-08 13:27:33', '2014-06-08 13:27:33', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/starcraft-2-wings-of-liberty-walkthrough-part-1-liberation-day-commentary/', 0, 'post', '', 0);
