(4959, 5, '2014-06-10 16:33:48', '2014-06-10 16:33:48', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 7 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. Sin, having attacked the boat, sets its sights on Kilika... When the party arrive there, Yuna must perform one of her other duties as a summoner, the sending; which sends the souls of the departed on to the farplane where they can rest in peace forever...</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 7 - Summoner Duties', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-7-summoner-duties', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:33:48', '2014-06-10 16:33:48', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-7-summoner-duties/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4960, 5, '2014-06-10 16:35:02', '2014-06-10 16:35:02', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 8 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. We take on the Lord of Kilika woods, an interesting fiend called Ochu, and then head up towards the temple.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 8 - Lord Ochu &amp; Geneaux', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-8-lord-ochu-geneaux', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:35:02', '2014-06-10 16:35:02', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-8-lord-ochu-geneaux/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4961, 1, '2014-06-10 16:35:55', '2014-06-10 16:35:55', 'Na''Vi vs Vici Gaming - Game 3 (Summit LAN - WB Round 1)\r\n\r\nCasters: Merlini (@MerliniDota) Demon (@LiquidDemon) &amp; Bulba (@LiquidBulba)\r\n\r\nThe Summit is the BTS run LAN event from their Los Angeles studio on June 5-8 featuring Na''Vi, DK, Vici Gaming, Fnatic, EG, &amp; Na''Vi.USA!\r\n\r\nTune in on June 5-8 at http://www.twitch.tv/beyondthesummit\r\n\r\nbeyondthesummit,bts,beyond the summit,lddota,godz,godzstudios,ggnetgodz,ld,dota,dota2,dota 2,cast,commentary,casting,shoutcast,dk,navi,fnatic,na''vi,the summit,summit,bts summit,LAN mania,navi.usa,vici gaming,VG,DK coach,71,eg,evil geniuses,summit LAN', 'Na''Vi vs Vici Gaming - Game 3 (Summit LAN - WB Round 1)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4856-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:35:55', '2014-06-10 16:35:55', '', 4856, 'http://www.gameveins.com/4856-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(4962, 5, '2014-06-10 16:37:50', '2014-06-10 16:37:50', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 9 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. Having dealt with the Sinspawn, we head in to the temple, where we meet a fellow Blitzball team called The Douchebags, and a summoner who seems to think that this whole pilgrimage is just a game...</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 9 - Dona &amp; Barthello', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-9-dona-barthello', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:37:50', '2014-06-10 16:37:50', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-9-dona-barthello/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4963, 5, '2014-06-10 16:39:04', '2014-06-10 16:39:04', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 10 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. Tidus and the crew leave Kilika to set sail for Luca. On the boat Tidus has a flashback of his father and his Jecht shot. He attempts to master it, and the onlooking Yuna reveals that it isn''t the first time she has seen the shot.. We then arrive in Luca, where the Aurochs are given a warm welcome...<br />Al Bhed Primer V is in this video.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 10 - Jecht Shot Mastery', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-10-jecht-shot-mastery', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:39:04', '2014-06-10 16:39:04', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-10-jecht-shot-mastery/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4964, 5, '2014-06-10 16:43:20', '2014-06-10 16:43:20', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 11 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. As the team prepare for the tournament, Yuna tells Tidus that Auron has been spotted in a cafe, much to his surprise. Vowing to return before the match starts, Tidus, Lulu, Yuna and Kimahri head to the cafe to find him.<br />Al Bhed Primer''s 6 &amp; 7 are in this video.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 11 - City Of Luca', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-11-city-of-luca', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:43:20', '2014-06-10 16:43:20', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-11-city-of-luca/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4965, 5, '2014-06-10 16:44:19', '2014-06-10 16:44:19', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 12 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. Yuna has been kidnapped by the Al Bhed, and it''s up to Tidus, Lulu and Kimahri to save her. They make their way to the dock where she is being held, and find themselves face to face with a large Machina Weapon, Oblitzerator.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 12 - Oblitzerator', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-12-oblitzerator', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:44:19', '2014-06-10 16:44:19', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-12-oblitzerator/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4966, 5, '2014-06-10 16:47:35', '2014-06-10 16:47:35', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 13 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. A nice long episode here where I attempt to defeat the Luca Goers and bring the Crystal Cup to Besaid for the first time in Wakka''s career.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 13 - Luca Goers Blitz Match', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-13-luca-goers-blitz-match', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:47:35', '2014-06-10 16:47:35', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-13-luca-goers-blitz-match/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4967, 5, '2014-06-10 16:49:02', '2014-06-10 16:49:02', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 14 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. Tidus and Wakka don''t get too much time to celebrate their victory, because a horde of fiends break into the stadium. Despite their best efforts, and a timely reunion with Auron, the stadium is overrun. This is where Seymour comes in, and uses his ridiculously cool looking and powerful aeon, Anima to kick some ass. Oh, and there''s a massive bombshell.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 14 - Anima Emerges', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-14-anima-emerges', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:49:02', '2014-06-10 16:49:02', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-14-anima-emerges/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4968, 5, '2014-06-10 16:50:37', '2014-06-10 16:50:37', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 15 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. We witness an interesting attempt by Yuna to add some laughter to her journey, then head to the Mihen Highroad, a place full of random encounters, NPC''s that give you things and an old man who loves to tell stories.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 15 - Laugh Out Loud', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-15-laugh-out-loud', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:50:37', '2014-06-10 16:50:37', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-15-laugh-out-loud/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4969, 5, '2014-06-10 16:54:34', '2014-06-10 16:54:34', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 16 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. Tidus and the gang run into a fellow summoner by the name of Belgemine. She instantly recognises Yuna as the daughter of high summoner Braska and decides it would be a good idea for them to have a duel to see who''s aeons are stronger. She subsequently kicks my ass :|</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 16 - Belgemine Kicks Ass', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-16-belgemine-kicks-ass', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:54:34', '2014-06-10 16:54:34', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-16-belgemine-kicks-ass/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4970, 5, '2014-06-10 16:56:21', '2014-06-10 16:56:21', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 17 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. The trek up the Mihen Highroad continues, and the gang rest up at an Al Bhed inn, much to Wakka''s annoyance. Tidus and Yuna learn more about each other and Tidus pledges his allegiance to the course, vowing to see Zanarkand with his own eyes. When they wake up the next morning, the Chocobo Eater fiend that was mentioned earlier is in the area and terrorizing the poor Chocobos yet again, and the gang make their final preparations before taking him down.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 17 - Warm Sunset', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-17-warm-sunset', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:56:21', '2014-06-10 16:56:21', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-17-warm-sunset/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4971, 5, '2014-06-10 16:57:55', '2014-06-10 16:57:55', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 18 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. Tidus and the gang take care of the troublesome Chocobo Eater, then get to ride a chocobo for free as a reward.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 18 - Chocobo Eater', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-18-chocobo-eater', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:57:55', '2014-06-10 16:57:55', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-18-chocobo-eater/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4972, 5, '2014-06-10 16:59:03', '2014-06-10 16:59:03', '<p>One of the slightly less entertaining parts of the game...<br />Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 19 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. The gang make it to Mushroom Rock Road, and Seymour delivers a rousing speech to the crusaders, spurring them on and showing his support. This surprises Wakka, and Seymour''s nonchalant responses confuse him even more. It''s then a trek up the Mushroom Rock Road towards the command centre, with plenty of random battles.</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 19 - Mushroom Rock Road', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-19-mushroom-rock-road', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:59:03', '2014-06-10 16:59:03', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-19-mushroom-rock-road/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4973, 5, '2014-06-10 16:59:57', '2014-06-10 16:59:57', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 20 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. We make it to the end of the Mushroom Rock Road, find Al Bhed Primer number 10, and watch Wakka punch someone in the face... Hard...</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 20 - Wakka''s Right Hook', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-20-wakkas-right-hook', '', '', '2014-06-10 16:59:57', '2014-06-10 16:59:57', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-20-wakkas-right-hook/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(4974, 5, '2014-06-10 17:01:03', '2014-06-10 17:01:03', '<p>Full Playlist: http://goo.gl/vvE6Vt<br />Welcome to part 21 of a commentary playthrough I will be doing for the remastered edition of Final Fantasy X. Operation Mihen commences, and it only takes about 15 seconds for a major fail to occur. It''s up to Yuna and her guardians to clean up the mess and defeat Sinspawn Gui...</p>', 'Final Fantasy X HD Remaster - Commentary Walkthrough - Part 21 - Sinspawn Gui', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-21-sinspawn-gui', '', '', '2014-06-10 17:01:03', '2014-06-10 17:01:03', '', 0, 'http://www.gameveins.com/final-fantasy-x-hd-remaster-commentary-walkthrough-part-21-sinspawn-gui/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
